boil the billy
Homonym Number:
Word Class: phrase
Sense Number:
Definition:to make tea in a billy; to stop for a smoko or tea and a snack
Origin: [none]
Register:
Register 2:
Domain: [none]
Region: [none]
See: billy, boil n., brew up
Pronunciation:
Notes:
